===========================================================================

plex86 has been compiled, but must be run in-place for now. To do so, do:

 * su
 * cd work*/plex86/.
 * cd misc
 * modload -e plex86_lkmentry -p netbsd_post.sh ../kernel/plex86.o
 * mkfontdir `pwd`
 * xset fp+ `pwd`
 * cd ../conf
 * Set up a config file (manuall edit necessary!)
 * cd ../user
 * ./plex86 -f ../conf/yourconfigfile

===========================================================================
